raw.reasoning: Run-level log view was gated while the workflow was still marked in progress, but job-level logs were directly accessible and showed the failing dependency path.

retrospective.summary: Identified failing workflow causes: x86_64 build cannot resolve local relaycast path dependency in CI checkout; aarch64 build additionally failed downloading musl cross toolchain from musl.cc.
